remarks: A strictly monotonic ordinal function on the set of natural numbers is one-to-one.  (Contributed by NM, 30-Nov-2003.)  (Revised by David Abernethy, 1-Jan-2014.)
statement:
omsmo $p |- ( ( ( A C_ On /\ F : _om --> A ) /\ A. x e. _om ( F ` x ) e. ( F ` suc x ) ) -> F : _om -1-1-> A ) $.
$d F x $.
